    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend trip, this car is ready to go! It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so you\u2019re getting a great vehicle that still looks and feels fantastic. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 32500.0,
