    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-revving power plant utilizes six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Engagement is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and the factory variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains sharp, benefitting from aluminum multi-link rear geometry and a front strut tower brace. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and a thorough subframe reinforcement inspection, ensuring the structural and mechanical integrity required for spirited driving. While the exterior displays minor road patina, the drivetrain remains mechanically sound and responsive.",
      "price": 34500.0,
