    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of luxury and dependability. The exterior maintains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small hairline scratch near the rear wheel well, both consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is a pristine, smoke-free environment featuring supple leather seating that shows only minimal signs of gentle wear on the driver's side bolster. Every electronic feature, from the intuitive dual-zone climate control to the premium surround-sound system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car has been fastidiously maintained with a documented service history; the engine runs quietly and the transmission shifts with seamless precision. It recently underwent a full multi-point inspection and received a fresh oil change, ensuring it is road-ready for its next owner. With its combination of a smooth ride and a well-cared-for interior, this car offers a refined driving experience that stands out in its class.",
      "price": 34500.0,
